column5: Only thing I wear that's fishing related would be my GLoomis ballcap..
Some thought it was lovely that my purse (tackle bag) matched my outfit...
Prolly not my first thought for keeping my beer cold.  JF
Usually just a Spider Wire cap and a metal t-shirt, or my scrubs.    It's too bad most fishing apparel is so tasteless.
Nice looking refridgerator....i wonder if its energy efficient
Ahhhh yessss ... the old Neoprene thong trick

BAHAHA! no not i! that is my buddy dave! ya hes a little different as you can see! we are there fishing and hes like hey guys you should see the thong im wearing! and we are like what the hell!?!?! and hes like check it out guys and well there you have it! it was quite funny! thank god i dont have pictures of my buddy mike, lets just say he loves to be naked LOL!
